      <section eId="sec_62">
        <num>62</num>
        <heading>Size of type</heading>
        <content>
          <p>  ยง 62. Size of type. Whenever a requirement of law relating to size of\ntype is stated in point size, the type size requirement shall be deemed\nmet if the x-height of the type is a minimum of forty-five percent of\nthe specified point size. Each point shall be measured as .351\nmillimeter. The x-height size shall be measured as it appears on the\npage. The x-height is the height of the lower case letters, exclusive of\nascenders or descenders.\n</p>
        </content>
      </section>
